WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Your will covers the house and the car.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
It doesn't cover the phone.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:18.000
The digital life you actually live — accounts, devices, logins,

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:25.000
the memories people will want — doesn't pass on with a signature.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:33.000
That's the gap. And it's a fixable one.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Not with a lawyer. Not with a weekend. With a playbook.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:56.000
My Final Playbook asks you a handful of plain-language questions —

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:05.000
no jargon, about five minutes — and shows you exactly where your plan stands.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:12.000
Then it hands you your first steps. Real actions with real instructions.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:25.000
Set a legacy contact. Name your beneficiaries. Put the important things in one place.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Jesse helps you along the way. He's learning this stuff too,

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:40.000
and he asks the questions you were already thinking.

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:48.000
Go further and it works through the whole thing with you. Every step tracked.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:55.000
A finished playbook your family will actually be able to use.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Live fully. Die ready. Get My Final Playbook.
